# 💼 React Job Portal (Frontend Only)

## 📌 Description

This project is a **React-based job portal** that allows users to browse, search, and apply for jobs, with all data handled on the frontend using localStorage.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🏠 Home page with navigation
* 📋 Job listing page
* 🔍 Search jobs by title
* 📄 Job details page
* 📝 Apply form (name, email, phone, resume UI)
* 💾 Stores applications in localStorage
* 🎨 Clean and responsive UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* React (JavaScript library)
* React Router
* JavaScript (ES6)
* CSS
* localStorage (for data storage)

---

